# Coding Standards

## Event vs State
- Always decide: STATE (R3) or EVENT (MessagePipe)

## Naming
- Events: past tense
- State: nouns/adjectives

## Forbidden
- UI publishing events
- Domain depending on R3 or MessagePipe
